<p>
<b>Pygame</b> is a set of <a href="http://www.python.org">Python</a>
modules designed for writing games. It is written on top
of the excellent <a href="http://www.libsdl.org">SDL</a> library.
This allows you to create fully featured games and multimedia
programs in the python language.
<b>Pygame</b> is highly portable and runs on nearly
every platform and operating system.
</p>

<p>
For a nice introduction to pygame, examine the <a href="/docs/tut/chimp/ChimpLineByLine.html">line-by-line chimp tutorial</a>, and the <a href="http://www.pygame.org/docs/tut/intro/intro.html">introduction for python programmers</a>.
</p>

